# Code Style for JS, TS, JSX, TSX

- "web" code is linted according to eslint (./eslint.config.js)
- "web" code is formatted according to BiomeJS (./web/biome.json)
- Semicolons are only used "as-needed"
- Default "tab" spacing is 2 spaces
- single quotes '' preferred
- trailing commas use 'es5' conditions
- within `./web`, run `pnpm run format` to re-format
- within `./web`, run `pnpm run lint` to lint
- within `./web`, validate the build with `pnpm run build`
